ing facilities, compassionate staff members, offering pet care. Their services creates a safe environment for play and exercise. centrally located for Brooklyn residents. Reach out to Brooklyn Pawffice for a consultation\",\"slug\":\"brooklyn-pawffice-brooklyn\",\"address\":\"522 Grand St\",\"street\":\"522 Grand St\",\"city\":\"Brooklyn\",\"state\":\"NY\",\"zipCode\":\"11211\",\"full_address\":\"522 Grand St, Brooklyn, NY 11211\",\"latitude\":40.7108524,\"longitude\":-73.9504695,\"googlePlaceId\":\"ChIJb_FfV3JbwokRYaKA05Q5QgI\",\"phone\":\"+1 929-258-8350\",\"website\":\"http://brooklynpawffice.com/\",\"photos\":null,\"rating\":4.9,\"reviewCount\":130,\"userRatingsTotal\":130,\"pricing\":{\"pricingSource\":\"unknown\",\"isFree\":false},\"placeTypes\":[\"point_of_interest\",\"establishment\"],\"dataQuality\":\"verified\",\"photo\":null,\"openingHours\":{\"Monday\":\"6AM-8PM\",\"Tuesday\":\"6AM-8PM\",\"Wednesday\":\"6AM-8PM\",\"Thursday\":\"6AM-8PM\",\"Friday\":\"6AM-8PM\",\"Saturday\":\"8AM-6PM\",\"Sunday\":\"8AM-6PM\"},\"faqs\":[],\"amenities\":{\"handicapAccess\":true,\"daycare\":true},\"source\":\"static\",\"listingType\":\"free\"},{\"id\":\"ChIJI_POKWBawokRaMLyyLmLZ4E\",\"name\":\"Brooklyn Sluggers\",\"businessType\":\"Dog Park\",\"description\":\"Brooklyn Sluggers has earned its reputation as Brooklyn's premier pet facility. This facility features professional grooming stations, compassionate staff members, offering pet care. Their services offers peace of mind for busy pet parents. readily accessible to Brooklyn pet owners. Call +1 315-230-4222 to learn more about their services\",\"slug\":\"brooklyn-sluggers\",\"address\":\"80A Verona St\",\"street\":\"80A Verona St\",\"city\":\"Brooklyn\",\"state\":\"NY\",\"zipCode\":\"11231\",\"full_address\":\"80A Verona St, Brooklyn, NY 11231\",\"latitude\":40.6795743,\"longitude\":-74.008967,\"googlePlaceId\":\"ChIJI_POKWBawokRaMLyyLmLZ4E\",\"phone\":\"+1 315-230-4222\",\"website\":\"http://www.brooklynsluggers.com/\",\"